id: S03-T4-TaskCardComponent
title: Task Card Component
status: pending
type: feature
requires:
  - REACT_TS
---

## Objective
Build a component to display individual task details nicely within the sprint list.

## Requirements
- Create a `client/src/components/TaskCard.tsx` component.
- The component takes a single parsed task object as props.
- Display the task Title, ID, and Status.
- Use visual indicators (like badges or colors) to represent the status (e.g., pending, done) and type (e.g., feature, bug).
- Integrate this component inside the `SprintListComponent` tracks loop.
